            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-secondary-500 mr-2">✓</span> Horarios fijos</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-secondary-500 mr-2">✓</span> Tarifas económicas</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-secondary-500 mr-2">✓</span> WiFi gratuito</li>
